{"operationName":"pairs","variables":{},"query":"fragment PairFields on Pool {
  id
  tx
  liquidity
  swapFee
  totalSwapVolume
  totalSwapFee
  totalWeight
  swapFee
  holdersCount
  totalSupply: totalShares
  tokens {
    id
    symbol
    name
    decimals
    priceUSD
    address
    balance
    denormWeight
    __typename
  }
  __typename
}

query pairs {
  pairs: pools(first: 3, orderBy: liquidity, orderDirection: desc) {
    ...PairFields
    __typename
  }
}
"}
